<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
A new breed of mage...a Warlock's tale (moved from Gen. Discussion to this section)<P>I screamed. Blackness enveloped my eyes, and I felt blood running out of my tear ducts. Violent howls racked my mind and I thrashed to the ground, knocking over my ebony lantern and lighting my house on fire as a crimson flare. Some licks of flame tickled my modest leather garb and I ran stumbling towards my door, breaking through my window instead, shards of glass cutting my back as I collapsed several yards away from my now crumbling cottage. My body suddenly lifted from the ground, gripped by an unseen force, and it seemed the Dragon's minions were shredding my entrails. Ten thousand searing needles seemed to pierce every neuron in my brain, and I screamed so loudly...my voice shattered. Everything went silent. I heard the subtle cawing of a raven in the distant woods.<P>My hand convulsed, my heart began palpitating, and I knew this torment was far from over. "BY THE HONOR IN THE ALL-FATHER, WHOEVER NOW COMMANDS THIS LAND RELEASE ME FROM SUCH PAIN!!!" I cried, sobbing to the ground, wondering if the rest of humanity was suffering such wicked pains.<P>I was sick...my body infested with festering sores. My mouth was dry, cotton-dry, and I stared blankly at a rock formation several feet from my head. Blank. Nothingness. I am nothing. I am the Blank. The Blank nothing. I know nothing. If...I know something, then I know some things and not others...if...I...know everything, then I know all things, yet I know nothing of non-things...thus...in....knowing nothing...I am master of...my...self...knowing only myself...knowing the world through inner reflection...I...I am not hurt...my body...is...fine...why...is the sky suddenly the most azure shade I've ever witnessed? "Boy, I've told you many times to never touch my gold plated hauberk, you know my father.." Whose voice is that? I see no one around "...you've had way too many chances boy, prepare to suffer your..." whose voice is this??? I can...stand now...I actually feel refreshed like never before...my body...is alive with power, my mind so clear "Father please, I swear I will not disturb your..." a child? a child speaking...in danger..who? "no, father please, I beg..." I must get to the child, dear, my cottage, it is ashes and...how many days has it been? "get back here boy, I will show you that..." Where is the boy? I...know...where he is...I know...where...he....is...how! What? where did...instant knowing? I must be dreaming, I am but a mere farmer, no sorcerer. There. There to the east beyond the darkened pines. Im being guided through the woods...by...some higher force? No...my...self...myself...there...I've never been this way to the woods yet "Prepare to DIE!!!" A man there running after a boy with his crude axe! I....will...I AM IN YOUR MIND AND AM YOUR MASTER, CEASE YOUR ACTIONS OR I WILL DESTROY YOU WITH PURE WILL... The man, he appears stunned and looks around, did I just speak into his mind? What is happening to me? Oh my, he has seen me now...I...I...NO, YOU SHALL STEP NO FURTHER, YOUR MIND IS DISSOLVED, TO YOUR KNEES, BEND TO MY WILL MORTAL! The man, he has fallen to his knees, blood is pouring from his ears, he is limp. I...I........and suddenly I understood the truth of the world.<P>I carved a stave from a tree, donned simple garbs...and walked...into the distance...would I find others like me?...or am I to be...a teacher... "Have at thee!" a voice...there...towards the west "no, dear All-Father no...help someone help!" I...will not assist...it is...not my place...I do not want to be seen...it is time to vanish into the mountains and garner mastery...in secrecy...I must keep my head low...until I understand...and come to know...myself...<P>--------------------<P>"Do you think my being stronger or faster, has anything to do with my body...in this world?"<BR>--Morpheus<BR>The Matrix has us...lets kick its arse with etheric mind blasts!!!<BR>SB Warlock...nuff said
</FONT>
